0.1-alpha5
==========
* Press Escape to exit fullscreen
* Update keyboard shortcuts dialog to the new adaptive design
* Fix album art cropped on pausing playback
* Flatpak: Fix re-opening the same file not working as intended
* Migrate playback history from custom CSV file to an Sqlite database

0.1-alpha4
==========
* Hide cursor on fullscreen
* Flatpak: Fix cover image not working in system player controls
* Allow side-by-side installations of Dev, Beta, Stable
* Update dev flatpak manifest

0.1-alpha3
==========
* Fix unintended cursor motion actions

0.1-alpha2
==========
* Fix wrong app name on Welcome screen
* Load AboutDialog from metainfo (appdata)

0.1-alpha
